data.description: Riverfront retreat on the beautiful Ochlockonee River! Wake up to spectacular sunrises, and enjoy the colors of sunsets over the water. Abundant wildlife just outside your door. Of course, world class fishing from your dock with 10,000 lb lift. Just 4 miles to the open Gulf.with nearby boat launch just across the river..Home offers 2 bedrooms and baths, open floor plan with large screened porch overlooking the river. Property abuts acres of state and trust owned forested land for your privacy. Convenient to St Marks Wildlife Refuge and the beaches of St Teresa.St George Island is a short drive away. Make this piece of paradise your vacation getaway or permanent home. Easy to show by appt only, please call to schedule. Sellers have other plans and have priced to sell!
